OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1781622677
OL,3,CMore than 80 patients affected by
OL,4,Chospital air-con failure
OL,6,FA total of 83 patients had their
OL,7,Fsurgeries postponed after air
OL,8,Fconditioning failed at Jersey's
OL,9,FGeneral Hospital during the recent
OL,10,Fheatwave.
OL,12,FSimon West, the Medical Director for
OL,13,FHealth and Care Jersey, says those
OL,14,Faffected were booked in for "routine,
OL,15,Fnon-urgent procedures" and have all
OL,16,Fbeen offered new dates.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
