OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1781622677
OL,3,CMore than 80 patients affected by
OL,4,Chospital air-con failure
OL,6,FHe adds the issue - which temporarily
OL,7,Fclosed three operating theatres during
OL,8,Flate May's record temperatures - has
OL,9,Fbeen resolved, with services returning
OL,10,Fto normal.
OL,12,FMr West explains: "Thanks to the swift
OL,13,Fand coordinated work of our teams, we
OL,14,Fwere able to implement an effective
OL,15,Flocal solution more quickly than first
OL,16,Fanticipated, allowing theatre activity
OL,17,Fto resume sooner.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1781622677
OL,3,CMore than 80 patients affected by
OL,4,Chospital air-con failure
OL,6,F"A total of 83 patients were affected,
OL,7,Ffar fewer than initially anticipated
OL,8,Fdue to the incredible work of our
OL,9,Fteams."
OL,11,FThe Medical Director says that a
OL,12,Fdamaged chilled water unit on the
OL,13,Fhospital's roof has been replaced,
OL,14,F"restoring resilience to the system".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
