CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1781622677
OL,3,CMore than 80 patients affected by
OL,4,Chospital air-con failure
OL,6,FMr West thanked everyone for their
OL,7,Funderstanding and praised the
OL,8,Fcommitment of his colleagues, adding:
OL,9,F"Our priority throughout has been to
OL,10,Fmaintain patient safety and minimise
OL,11,Fdisruption, and I am confident we have
OL,12,Fachieved that while recovering
OL,13,Fservices quickly and safely."
OL,15,FThe Medical Director also laid blame
OL,16,Fat the "older facilities", stating "a
OL,17,Fpermanent long-term solution remains
OL,18,Fin progress and is in hand".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
