OL,3,CMore than 80 patients affected by
OL,4,Chospital air-con failure
OL,6,FIt comes as the Government of Jersey
OL,7,Fannounced that it has signed a
OL,8,Fcontract with the construction firm
OL,9,FBouygues UK to build the island's new
OL,10,Fhospital at Overdale after months of
OL,11,Fnegotiation.
OL,13,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,14,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,15,FChannel breaks down the key election
OL,16,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,17,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,18,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX, and YouTube
OL,19,Fbelow, with new episodes each
OL,20,FThursday...
